<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>默认情况下</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US>
     SpringBoot </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>对返回的数据有以下对应的返回类型，如果没有对数据进行统一，前端获取到数据时就不能很好的进行处理</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in'><img
src="data:image/png;base64,"
width=627 height=149></p>

<p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>因此在以前的开发中我们会定义统一的</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> Result </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>响应体和</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US>
     ResultCode </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>错误码，使用</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>Result.success()</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>，</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>Result.</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US>fail</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>()</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>来封装成统一的响应体返回数据，无论请求成功还是错误，都统一返回三个基本数据。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>但是这种方式在错误响应体的封装下</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> data </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>值会显示为</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> null </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>值，实际的场景中错误响应体是不需要返回数据的，将错误信息传递到</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> data </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>也是不安全的，错误统一由全局错误处理类返回预定义的错误码和消息即可。如果取消对</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> null </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>值序列化处理处理，也会导致一些潜在的问题。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>这时我们需要将响应体分离，建立成功响应体和错误响应体，分别在其中定义所需的数据，同时加上</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>status</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>属性显示地标识响应体的请求逻辑</span></li>
</ul>
